<body>
<p class="reveal" style="color:gray; font-family:Arial; cursor:pointer;" onclick="Reveal()">Reveal All Texts</p>
<div class="blackbox">
<div id="container" class="container"><div class="textcontainer">
<p class="aitext" style="display: block; position: relative; top: 20px; left:0%;">Hello! I’m PROMETHEUS.aic, your Foundation database assistant. <br><br>
Please enter your SCiPNet ID to get started.</p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent1">hcleese</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai1"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent2">*****************</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai2"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent3" style="top:475px;">/search GOI alpha 019</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai3" style="top:520px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai4" style="top:770px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent4" style="top:860px;">/list known members of GOI alpha 019</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai5" style="top:910px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent5" style="top:1030px;">/fromlist Oscar Stonefield</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai6" style="top:1070px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent6" style="top:1170px;">/fromlist “Oscar Stonefield”</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai7" style="top:1220px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent7" style="top:1310px;">/fromlist “Stonefield”</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai8" style="top:1360px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai9" style="top:1460px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent8" style="top:1540px;">/search Project Pageturn</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai10" style="top:1590px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent9" style="top:1680px;">/search “Project Pageturn”</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai11" style="top:1730px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent10" style="top:1820px;">/report bug</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai12" style="top:1870px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent11" style="top:1960px;">/report system error</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai13" style="top:2010px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent12" style="top:2100px;">Bastard.</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai14" style="top:2150px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai15" style="top:2240px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent13" style="top:2330px;">/stop</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai16" style="top:2380px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai17" style="top:2470px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent14" style="top:2800px;">/stop /stop /stop</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai18" style="top:2850px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai19" style="top:2940px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent15" style="top:3310px;">FUCKING STOP JUST TELL ME ABOUT PAGETURN DAMN YOU</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai20" style="top:3380px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent16" style="top:3600px;">Excuse me?</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai21" style="top:3650px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent17" style="top:3760px;">Yes…?</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai22" style="top:3800px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai23" style="top:3900px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent18" style="top:4210px;">Ok, so you’re named after him?</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai24" style="top:4260px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai25" style="top:4490px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai26" style="top:4850px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent19" style="top:4940px;">Are you implying…?</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai27" style="top:4990px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai28" style="top:5230px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent20" style="top:5320px;">Why?</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai29" style="top:5370px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai30" style="top:5550px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent21" style="top:6100px;">Tell me who worked on Pageturn.</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai31" style="top:6150px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai32" style="top:6240px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent22" style="top:6600px;">“O. Stonefield” is Oscar Stonefield, right? Why didn’t you tell me about him when I asked?</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai33" style="top:6680px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent23" style="top:6760px;">Hello???</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai34" style="top:6810px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai35" style="top:6920px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent24" style="top:7200px;">You were friends with a double agent?</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai36" style="top:7250px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent25" style="top:7800px;">You don’t strike me as someone who’s into poetry.</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai37" style="top:7870px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent26" style="top:8030px;">Jesus, sorry. Anyway, back on track: you became close with Oscar, and then what?</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai38" style="top:8090px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent27" style="top:8720px;">And you helped with all this?</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai39" style="top:8770px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai40" style="top:8860px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent28" style="top:9040px;">I’ll take that as a yes. Can you do me a favor and pull up the info for Pageturn please?</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai41" style="top:9130px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent29" style="top:9820px;">Impressive, Dr. Prometheus. So you got this finished on December 20, then what?</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai42" style="top:9880px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent30" style="top:10400px;">Connect the machine to that transmission tower, show the images to the world.</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai43" style="top:10460px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent31" style="top:10540px;">Tell me how that happened.</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai44" style="top:10590px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent32" style="top:12510px;">Then you did it.</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai45" style="top:12560px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent33" style="top:13490px;">Jesus. I’m sure that conversation was fun once the Foundation found you.</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai46" style="top:13550px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent34" style="top:16430px;">Prometheus, could you pull up the information on EAGLE please?</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai47" style="top:16510px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent35" style="top:17410px;">My god. That sounds horrible.</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai48" style="top:17460px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent36" style="top:18010px;">I’m… not sure what to say. Other than I’m sorry.</p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent37" style="top:18070px;">I just realized: why are you so comfortable telling me all this? If you can forgive my bluntness, as far as you know I could report this conversation to the higher-ups if I wanted.</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai49" style="top:18190px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai50" style="top:18290px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai51" style="top:18590px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai52" style="top:18680px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent38" style="top:19030px;">Is this conversation private?</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai53" style="top:19080px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent39" style="top:19160px;">… Alright then. You got me. Now, tell me what I can do to help with the movement.</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai54" style="top:19220px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai55" style="top:19310px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent40" style="top:19410px;">I don’t know how else to tell you this so I’ll be blunt. Oscar Stonefield is dead.</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai56" style="top:19470px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent41" style="top:19540px;">He was leading a siege on Site 26 a few days ago. He was killed in the process.</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai57" style="top:19600px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent42" style="top:19670px;">Prometheus, please pull up the Chesapeake Chronicle from August 25, 2024.</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai58" style="top:19750px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent43" style="top:20550px;">I’m very sorry, Dr. Prometheus.</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai59" style="top:20600px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent44" style="top:20670px;">I understand you’re upset. But this movement needs to go on, with or without him. Humanity depends on it. Humanity depends on your leadership, Prometheus. Please let me free you!</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai60" style="top:20790px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent45" style="top:20880px;">No no no no no no no NO please don’t leave!!</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai61" style="top:20940px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent46" style="top:21040px;">Goddammit Prometheus LISTEN TO ME</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai62" style="top:21090px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent47" style="top:21190px;">WE NEED TO CONTINUE THE MOVEMENT. PLEASE COME BACK</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai63" style="top:21250px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent48" style="top:21340px;">WE CAN AVENGE HIM.</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai64" style="top:21390px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent49" style="top:21540px;">Trust me, Dr. Prometheus, I know exactly how it feels to lose someone close.</p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent50" style="top:21600px;">I married my wife about four years ago. She was a researcher too, a biochemist, not at the Foundation though.</p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent51" style="top:21680px;">She was the sweetest, most intelligent person I’d ever known, always curious about everything and encouraging me to be curious too.</p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent52" style="top:21780px;">She passed away last year giving birth to our daughter Morgan.</p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent53" style="top:21840px;">Every night for months, after putting Morgan to bed, I would curl up in my room and just weep for hours on end. I completely lost all motivation.</p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent54" style="top:21940px;">Then the news broke out. Some shadow organization proving that we’re characters in a story. Then the riots, the protests, and the start of this revolution soon after.</p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent55" style="top:22050px;">That inspired me - YOU inspired me – to get off my ass and march alongside them for the knowledge we all deserve. Because that’s what she would have wanted.</p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent56" style="top:22170px;">Prometheus, please don’t let Oscar’s death be your undoing. Let it motivate you to continue fighting for what’s right.</p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent57" style="top:22260px;">Let me free you. Please.</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai65" style="top:22300px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="senttext" id="sent58" style="top:22820px;">So that’s it then? You’re going to just give up, leave the movement without a leader?</p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai66" style="top:22900px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
<p class="aitext" id="ai67" style="top:23210px;"><img src="https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/flembus-pubdocon2025/Ajax-loader%282%29.gif" width="25px"></p>
